id: 00001007720600
title: Query: Ident Directive
role: manual
tags: #manual #search #zettelstore
syntax: zmk
created: 20230724153018
modified: 20260609122419

An ident directive is needed if you want to specify just a list of zettel identifiers.
It starts with the keyword ''IDENT''.

When not using the ident directive, zettel identifier are interpreted as a [[search expression|00001007701000]].